dc_title_s: Pierhead and bulkhead lines, Hackensack River, N.J., from Gas Works Creek to Anderson St. Bridge, Hackensack, Bogota and Teaneck
dc_description_s: Map showing property and company lines along the Hackensack River, approved by the Department of War|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Drawn by E.F.M. & W.B.M.|File No. Hackensack Rv 1/74.|Soundings are depths in feet at mean low water|The street systems are compiled from assessment maps of the City of Hackensack, Borough of Bogota and Township of Teaneck.|Map contains inset index map of harbor line maps for Hackensack River at top.|Map contains thirteen inset descriptive diagrams of monuments and reference points in top left corner.
